I had some trouble installing Anno 1404 & the addon, Venice, so I decided to write up easy to follow instructions! This is how I installed it, so if this doesn't work for you, don't blame me! Thanks to Razor1911, thenoobish, everyone who seeds, & most of all, Ubisoft! If you like this game, you should buy it to support them!
Part 1 - Installing the game
1) Download Anno 1404 (http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/4990931/Anno_1404_Dawn_Of_Discovery-Razor1911) 
2) Open the folder
3) Right click the very first file in the folder ('rzr-144a', it's a 001 file) & open it with WinRAR (or whatever program you have)
4) Select 'extract to' & pay attention to what folder you're extracting to!
5) Open that folder, & you'll see an ISO file
6) Open that file using VirtualCloneDrive, or another suitable mounting program
7) Run that drive, as you would a normal CD or DVD & install the game
Part 2 - Cracking the game
1) Download the crack (http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/4990932/Anno_1404_Dawn_Of_Discovery-Razor1911-Crack)
2) Open the folder
3) Open the folder 'Razor1911'
4) Copy the 'Anno4' EXE to your Anno 1404 main folder (if you installed it in the default location, it'll be in Program Files > Ubisoft > Related Designs > ANNO 1404), overwriting the original EXE
5) Click on this new EXE to play the game! (Or, continue to install the addon Venice)
Part 3 - Installing Venice
1) Download the addon (http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5392711/Anno.1404.Venice-RELOADED)
2) Open the folder
3) Select all the WinRAR files & right-click & select 'Extract Here' 
4) This will create another ISO file, which you run with VirtualCloneDrive, or whatever
5) Run that drive, as you would a normal CD or DVD & install the game
6) It will patch Anno 1404 before installing, so don't worry if it takes a while to bring up the actual installation process
7) Go to your Anno 1404 main folder (if you installed it in the default location, it'll be in Program Files > Ubisoft > Related Designs > ANNO 1404) again, & click 'addon.exe' 
8) Select 'Manual'
9) Copy the 'Hardware ID'
10) Go to My Computer, right-click the mounted ISO image & select 'Explore'
11) Open the 'Crack' folder, run the 'keygen.exe'
12) Paste your Hardware ID into the box & click 'Generate'
13) Copy the Activation Key in the Activator & click next
14) The game will launch & you're ready to play!

READ THIS!!  Works Windows 7 x64.  Can't find the keygen?  It's because your anti-virus quarantined it automatically.  Your av doesn't lie - IT IS A TROJAN and it will DESTROY your system!  Your anti-virus program and windows update will be fucked.  What to do?  Save your system image on a usb drive.  Disable your av and run the damn keygen.  Get the key and save it to a text file and save that on your usb.  Restore your system from the image and now you can play cuz you have the code and didn't open a trojan.

You can do this with any other infected keygen or program - run it and see what it does and then revert to your image.  Always make an image before you do anything 'dangerous' and ALWAYS install ALL your software on a different hard drive.  This decreases the size of your system image and also makes it easier for your computer to find the data, thus increasing your system's performance dramatically.
